# Force LF line endings on all text files in the published OSS tree.
# Rationale: oss-scrub.cjs applyHeader() inserts header lines using \n; mixing
# with CRLF source files would produce inconsistent endings. Since downstream
# users may clone on Windows, this attribute ensures Git checks out text as LF
# and refuses to mix endings inside one file.

* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary types that must never be normalized.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.eot binary
*.zip binary
*.pdf binary
*.mp3 binary
*.mp4 binary
*.wasm binary
*.wav binary
*.ogg binary
*.tar binary
*.gz binary
*.bz2 binary
*.xz binary
*.7z binary
